{StudioExec}
Don't sound so scared, it's a little one. Just a small one. You familiar with the Joey Dinger show?

[[I don't think so.|explain2]]

{StudioExec}
That's no surprise. It's a real stinker of a talk show. We gotta sandwich it between two top-rated shows just to get people to watch the damn thing - it's a real hammock-job.

[[I'm listening..|okay]]
